OL,3,CHomes evacuated after reports of man
OL,4,Cbarricading himself inside property
OL,6,FMore than 20 homes have been evacuated
OL,7,Fafter reports a man has barricaded
OL,8,Fhimself into a property and is making
OL,9,Fthreats on Teesside.
OL,11,FCleveland Police officers are at the
OL,12,Fscene of an ongoing incident in
OL,13,FOsbourne Close, in Hemlington.
OL,15,FIt follows reports at around 7:30am on
OL,16,FThursday (25 June) that a man had
OL,17,Fbarricaded himself into a property and
OL,18,Fwas making threats.
OL,20,FOsbourne Close is a cul-de-sac near
OL,21,FHemlington Lake.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
