OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1782411503
OL,3,CHomes evacuated after reports of man
OL,4,Cbarricading himself inside property
OL,6,FSuperintendent Paul Allen said: "At
OL,7,Fthis time, we remain on the scene at
OL,8,FOsbourne Close and negotiations with
OL,9,Fthe man in the property are ongoing,
OL,10,Four priority is to bring this incident
OL,11,Fto safe conclusion.
OL,13,F"We have extended the cordon; this has
OL,14,Fresulted in more properties being
OL,15,Fevacuated. Middlesborough Council has
OL,16,Fset up a rest centre for anyone who
OL,17,Fhas been displaced, this can be
OL,18,Flocated at Hemlington Library.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
