PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1782411503
OL,3,CHomes evacuated after reports of man
OL,4,Cbarricading himself inside property
OL,6,F"I would like to reassure the
OL,7,Fcommunity that this is an isolated
OL,8,Fincident, in a single property. Any
OL,9,Fspecialist equipment and services,
OL,10,Fincluding the explosives unit, are at
OL,11,Fthe scene as a precaution at this
OL,12,Fstage."
